"UL104-FP004" and "G2-PI-0303-5X" is silkscreened on the top side of the board by the power and upstream port. :"UL104-G2" is silkscreened on the board by the downstream ports.
The '''[[Genesys Logic]]''' Hub IC is marked with "GL650USB" and "0324FGW4W-35".
